data.description: Come check out this renovated 3 bedroom 3 bathroom home! This home offers a cozy living area with all bedrooms on the main floor. Finished walk out basement with attached garage, great area for a secondary living space! HVAC is 2 years old! New stainless steel kitchen appliances. Bedrooms feature built in storage spaces. Updated bathrooms and flooring throughout the home. Yard space is great and plenty of parking with car port, garage, and drive way! Make this your home in time for the holiday season!
